51
00:09:17,444 --> 00:09:25,307
I want to talk about the barber car that was there when the roofs were leaking and she was running around with buckets to make sure she could keep the library open.

52
00:09:25,887 --> 00:09:35,935
or the person that needed to be reached because we need a community space, and Barbara would be the only person that would be helping our community make sure people could be heard.

53
00:09:36,495 --> 00:09:39,677
