56
00:09:45,822 --> 00:09:50,245
But Barbara's the type of person that goes above and beyond any paycheck.

57
00:09:51,722 --> 00:09:59,529
That's why I make the request that this council, Mr. President, finds a way that we do something right before it's time.

58
00:09:59,589 --> 00:10:11,939
I've seen too many great people of Medford that have given their lives to Medford, and then when they move on, we then decide that we should name something after them, and they're not there to celebrate it.

59
00:10:11,999 --> 00:10:16,663
I think it's time that we find a little corner of our new library

60
00:10:17,123 --> 00:10:23,447
that would have a plaque that has Barbara Kerr's name on it so everybody knows the impact that she's made.

61
00:10:23,507 --> 00:10:29,950
I mean, you know, I mean, our names are on the, a few of our names are on that wall.

62
00:10:30,431 --> 00:10:37,475
It's not Barbara Kerr's, but I tell you what, Barbara Kerr has gone above and beyond anything we've done, and our names are on that building.

63
00:10:37,535 --> 00:10:42,357
So it's a little embarrassing for someone like myself that has a name on a building

64
00:10:44,496 --> 00:10:56,363
to memorialize it, but someone like Barbara Kerr that's actually put the blood, the sweat, and the tears, and hopefully, you know, her name will live on far longer than will be here.

65
00:10:56,463 --> 00:11:00,206
So if we can, Mr. President, I would make the request that we

66
00:11:01,492 --> 00:11:11,661
