124
00:14:53,926 --> 00:15:04,735
Before starting work, the contractor shall notify DigSafe and obtain all operable permits including a public right of way occupancy permit pursuant to section 74141 of the city ordinances prior to commencing work.

125
00:15:05,736 --> 00:15:09,178
