But again, thank you for being here.

417
00:35:51,257 --> 00:35:51,937
Name and address, please.

418
00:35:52,666 --> 00:35:58,209
appreciate all of you for having us speak and to Councilor Leving in particular for your support.

419
00:35:58,989 --> 00:36:01,930
My name is Steve Meacham and I'm with the Housing Justice Alliance.

420
00:36:02,971 --> 00:36:07,153
We work with tenant associations in many communities, inner suburbs, including Medford.

421
00:36:08,133 --> 00:36:10,434
And one of those is the Brooks Park Tenant Association.

422
00:36:10,954 --> 00:36:16,837
We came here actually two years ago seeking support for our efforts to get a collective bargaining agreement.

423
00:36:16,897 --> 00:36:20,239
And just so you know, we won that partly due to your support.

424
00:36:21,019 --> 00:36:22,500
the things that you do make a difference.

425
00:36:24,401 --> 00:36:34,647
But we held that walking tour that Councillor Lemming referred to last week, and we've been just trying to fight this rat situation.

426
00:36:34,667 --> 00:36:36,588
I'm going to let our folks here talk about it.

427
00:36:37,929 --> 00:36:48,876
But even for me, I've been to countless meetings in the laundry room in the back of the building, and I've learned, don't walk back there unless you have a flashlight and are ready to make noise, because there's a lot of rats.

428
00:36:49,743 --> 00:36:53,145
So thank you for having us, and I'll let these guys introduce themselves.

429
00:36:54,386 --> 00:36:55,046
Thank you.

430
00:36:58,828 --> 00:36:59,388
Good evening.

431
00:36:59,649 --> 00:37:05,392
I am Julia Forster, and I have lived at Brooks Park in Medford for almost 24 years.

432
00:37:05,932 --> 00:37:08,513
I live in Building 8, Apartment 19.

433
00:37:09,134 --> 00:37:15,557
I am here this evening to discuss the rat population and to share with you how it is affecting my life.

434
00:37:16,178 --> 00:37:18,319
They do not pay rent like we do.

435
00:37:20,644 --> 00:37:22,764
I go outside to empty the trash.

436
00:37:23,085 --> 00:37:24,745
One hears them in the dumpsters.

437
00:37:25,005 --> 00:37:25,666
Click, click.

