700
01:01:08,757 --> 01:01:12,259
So whatever the value of one unit would be based on that,

701
01:01:12,999 --> 01:01:16,722
You would say, say it's 0.1 units, then take 10% of that.

702
01:01:17,363 --> 01:01:20,785
That amount could be then contributed into the Affordable Housing Trust.

703
01:01:21,266 --> 01:01:26,290
So you could either build the, you could round up, or you could make that contribution to the trust.

704
01:01:26,390 --> 01:01:34,097
