716
01:02:29,213 --> 01:02:44,825
So the benefits, as I mentioned, more housing is created overall, increasing revenue for the Affordable Housing Trust, and then with that increased revenue, the Affordable Housing Trust will have more available funds to support the creation of affordable housing in the future.

